            .row
              .col-md-12
                p. 
                  Project MoNET seeks to create a robot/web platform capable of manufacturing semi-abstract art based on environmental stimulus and crowd sourced data.
                  It is set to debut at #[a(href="http://makerfairepittsburgh.com/") Maker Faire Pittsburgh 2016].
      .col-md-2
  
