      .col-md-2
      .col-md-8.content
        h1 how it works
        p.
          Project MoNET will sample it's environment via a system of color sensors. It will then assemble these samples into an image and paint this to a canvas using a robotic brush.
        p.
          As an additional source of inspiration, MoNET will also paint based on aggregate color samples derived from crowd-submitted photographs.
        p Tech curious? #[a(href="#") Go deeper down the rabbit hole.]
      .col-md-2
    
    #color-wall.row
