        p. 
          The colorwall is MoNET's early technology demonstrator. It combines colors extracted from user submitted pictures and input from our color sensor network (assuming it&apos;s on)
          to create a virtual painting. 
        .text-center
          a.btn.btn-info.btn-lg.text-center(href="colorwall1") Check it out!
